title: CMT Made
overview: In CMT Made, CMT is giving adults the opportunity to chase their dreams! CMT Made will follow adults, rather than teens, as they embark on a mission to transform their life, highlighting both the challenges and accomplishments they face throughout their journey of being MADE.This eight-episode series follows adults, not teens, as they embark on a mission to transform their life, highlighting both the challenges and accomplishments they face throughout their journey of being MADE.
